than a mall Santa.

03:58.271 --> 04:00.373
<i>- Ho, ho, ho.</i>
- Oh, yeah.

04:00.407 --> 04:03.843
- All right, next tip:
goodie bags.

04:03.877 --> 04:06.613
They're presents other people
get, but if you have

04:06.646 --> 04:10.650
