keeps the leftovers.

04:10.684 --> 04:14.120
This birthday girl.

04:14.154 --> 04:18.058
And finally: the sugar crash.

04:18.058 --> 04:21.461
Avoid a birthday sugar crash
with this easy trick.

04:21.494 --> 04:24.497
Never stop eating sugar,
and you won't crash.

04:24.531 --> 04:26.066
Win-win.
<i>[bell dinging]</i>

04:26.099 --> 04:27.600
[cheers and applause]

04:27.634 --> 04:30.704
Follow our birthday handbook,
and you'll be celebrating

04:30.737 --> 04:33.106
