08:21.668 --> 08:24.504
- How valuable--and this
is gonna be weird to you--

08:24.537 --> 08:28.875
how valuable boredom is,
boredom and silence.

08:28.908 --> 08:30.677
- Yeah.
- Because oftentimes,

08:30.710 --> 08:31.911
especially now,

08:31.945 --> 08:35.048
the temptation to always
pull out our phones

08:35.081 --> 08:37.183
and entertain ourselves
every few seconds,

08:37.217 --> 08:39.953
that takes away
the thought process

08:40.053 --> 08:42.088
of where those ideas come.

08:42.122 --> 08:45.558
So usually an hour a day,
I literally like to sit

08:45.592 --> 08:48.828
in an isolated room
and get bored.

08:48.862 --> 08:51.831
